# Empty patches/ directory for future tinyhat-specific diffs.
#
# When the tinyhat platform needs to apply a small fix on top of the
# vendored upstream (e.g. a watchdog hook, a sandbox-network policy
# tweak), drop the patch file here as `NNNN-tinyhat-<short-name>.patch`
# and reference it in HARNESS.md so an external reader can see what
# we changed and why.
#
# At the v1 launch this directory is empty — the wrapper applies no
# patches.
